{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Bézier curve","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Bezier_curve","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>贝塞尔曲线</strong>是一种使用数学方法描述的曲线，被广泛用于计算机图形学和动画中，在 <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此页面仍未被本地化, 期待您的翻译!\">vector images</a> 里，贝塞尔曲线用于定义可无限放大的光滑曲线。</p>\n<p>贝塞尔曲线由至少两个控制点进行描述。Web 技术中使用的是三次贝塞尔曲线，即使用四个控制点 [P<sub>0</sub>, P<sub>1</sub>, P<sub>2</sub>, P<sub>3</sub>] 描述的曲线。</p>\n<p>在绘制曲线的过程中，需要先作两条辅助线：[P<sub>0</sub>,P<sub>1</sub> ] 和 [P<sub>1</sub> , P<sub>2</sub>]（译者注：下图中的绿线）；辅助线的端点沿着所在连线平滑地移动到连线的另一端；采用同样的方法在辅助线 [P<sub>0</sub>,P<sub>1</sub> ] 和 [P<sub>1</sub> , P<sub>2</sub>] 上绘制第三条辅助线（译者注：下图中的蓝线）；在第三条辅助线上将一个点从一端平滑地移向另外一端，这个点的运动轨迹就是贝塞尔曲线。下面是这个绘图过程的动态演示：</p>\n<p>\n  <img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/d/db/B%C3%A9zier_3_big.gif\" alt=\"Drawing a Bézier curve\" loading=\"lazy\">\n</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"了解更多","title":"了解更多","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"常识","title":"常识","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/B%C3%A9zier_curve\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Bézier curve on Wikipedia</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"学习使用贝塞尔曲线","title":"学习使用贝塞尔曲线","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/easing-function#the_cubic-bezier()_class_of_timing_functions\">Cubic Bézier timing functions in CSS</a></li>\n  <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/keySplines\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">keySplines (en-US)</a></code> SVG attribute</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/Tools/Cubic_Bezier_Generator\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">Cubic Bézier Generator</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"了解更多","id":"了解更多"}],"summary":"贝塞尔曲线是一种使用数学方法描述的曲线，被广泛用于计算机图形学和动画中，在 vector images 里，贝塞尔曲线用于定义可无限放大的光滑曲线。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Bézier curve","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Courbe de Bézier","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Bézier curve (ベジェ曲線)","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Кривая Безье","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/glossary/bezier_curve","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/glossary/bezier_curve/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary","title":"术语表"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Bezier_curve","title":"Bézier curve"}],"pageTitle":"Bézier curve - 术语表 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}